data.description: Wonderful 2/1 cottage home on large lot,0624 acres completely fenced. Recently renovated. Awesome chef's kitchen with teak countertops. Large main bedroom with a seating area. 2nd bedroom or office that has an entrance to private covered patio. Covered patio stretches the complete front of house, another patio off the kitchen to the backyard. 1 storage shed with carport, 2nd shed with well and storage, and a large tool shed, all wired. All newer appliances convey. Generator hookups. Motivated !
